headline.main: News from Havana and Mexico.; FEARFUL STORM OFF VERA CRUZ--TWO MEN-OF- WAR WRECKED AND EIGHTY LIVES LOST--COMMERCIAL NEWS.

docs.lead_paragraph: The steamship lsabel, from Havana and Key West on the 10th inst., has arrived hero. The health of Dr. KANE was improving. A great storm had occurred off Vera Cruz, Numerous vessels wore wrecked, including the ship-ofwar Guadaloupe and steamer Iturbide. Eighty persons on board the latter were lost.
